<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>92</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<title>Hallelujah</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hallelujah aw, Hallelujah Amen,
 Kalvari hehpihna thisan zalin;
 Kahna gam leh lungngaihna zan thim hi,
 Nawpna van pielgal khun a salh vak.

[V2]
 Kipahna chullo ding,
 Hallelujah, Hallelujah!
 Chawihatin um zing hen Belam No chu,
 A hehpihna chun lungngaih a nem.

[V3]
 2. Aw, Thagau lengin kipahna gimlim,
 &quot;Hallelujah&quot; ti'n zie gamthip ahin;
 Kipakin a awi ui gimthei chate'n,
 Nang na um leh lei van gam a chang.

[V4]
 3. Kumkhaw gam leh kumsawt a beih masieh,
 Nawpna vak lopi van Saron pak hawih;
 Aw na lunlai ni hi bei ta puon a,
 Nang ka ngai pen ie ei umpih in.

[V5]
 4. Aw khawvel in he leu ka Lal lopi,
 Van Angel lak ah lawp na tha zakin;
 Kalvari Belam No hehpihna hi,
 Awiin sau in tin a kumsawt in.</lyrics>
</song>